title: Highway to Heaven - S01E18 - A Child of God
description:
18. A Child of God   
Community Score
7.4 Good
First aired: 2/6/1985

Jonathan and Mark try to reunite a father and daughter who hadn&#039;t seen each other in years because of the daughter 
had a child from own without a husband. Now Jonathan has a difficult task of trying to convince the father that he 
doesn&#039;t have a lot of time to get to know his daughter Marsha because she is terminally ill.

Writer: Michael Landon
Director: Michael Landon
Guest star: Paula Martin (Patient), Bill Sorrells (Doctor), Nora Boland (Mrs. Hardy), Jerome Thor (Dr. Gottlleb), 
William Windom (Reverend Stearns), Colleen Maloney (Marsha), Patricia Smith (Sarah Sterns), Natalie Gregory 
(Amy)
